query: 計算各倉庫的總庫存量
sql:

    SUM(t2.img10) AS total_stock
FROM
    read_parquet('s3://tiptop-raw/raw/v1/img_file/year=*/month=*/data.parquet', hive_partitioning=true) t2
JOIN
    read_parquet('s3://tiptop-raw/raw/v1/imd_file/year=*/month=*/data.parquet') t3 ON t2.img02 = t3.imd01
GROUP BY

ORDER BY 1
LIMIT 50 OFFSET 0

query: 計算各倉庫的平均庫存量
sql:

    t3.imd01 AS warehouse_code,
    AVG(t2.img10) AS average_inventory
FROM
    read_parquet('s3://tiptop-raw/raw/v1/img_file/year=*/month=*/data.parquet', hive_partitioning=true) t2
JOIN
    read_parquet('s3://tiptop-raw/raw/v1/imd_file/year=*/month=*/data.parquet') t3 ON t2.img02 = t3.imd01
GROUP BY
    t3.imd01
ORDER BY

LIMIT 50 OFFSET 0

query: 查詢生產領料記錄
sql:
SELECT
    t6.tll01 AS leaders,
    t7.tlm03 AS items,
    t8.imd02 AS warehouses,
    t9.ima02 AS item_names,
    t6.tll04 AS quantities,
    t6.tll05 AS units,
    t6.tll06 AS dates
FROM
    read_parquet('s3://tiptop-raw/raw/v1/tll_file/year=*/month=*/data.parquet', hive_partitioning=true) t6
JOIN
    read_parquet('s3://tiptop-raw/raw/v1/tlm_file/year=*/month=*/data.parquet') t7 ON t6.tll02 = t7.tlm01
JOIN
    read_parquet('s3://tiptop-raw/raw/v1/imd_file/year=*/month=*/data.parquet') t8 ON t6.tll03 = t8.imd01
JOIN
    read_parquet('s3://tiptop-raw/raw/v1/ima_file/year=*/month=*/data.parquet') t9 ON t7.tlm02 = t9.ima01
WHERE
    t6.tll04 >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL 30 DAY

ORDER BY 1
LIMIT 50 OFFSET 0

query: 查詢某倉庫的交易趨勢
sql:
SELECT
    strftime(t4.tlf06, '%Y-%m') AS month,
    SUM(CASE WHEN t4.tlf19 = '入' THEN t4.tlf10 ELSE -t4.tlf10 END) AS trend
FROM
    read_parquet('s3://tiptop-raw/raw/v1/tlf_file/year=*/month=*/data.parquet', hive_partitioning=true) t4
JOIN
    read_parquet('s3://tiptop-raw/raw/v1/img_file/year=*/month=*/data.parquet') t2 ON t4.tlf01 = t2.img01
WHERE
    t2.img02 = 'W01'
GROUP BY
    month
ORDER BY
    month
LIMIT 50 OFFSET 0
